acceptance_criteria: "A local lint command reproduces the CodeFactor Maintainability findings (rule counts reconcile within tolerance); ESLint --fix mechanically clears the auto-fixable unicorn rules; a duplication check (e.g. jscpd) surfaces the Duplication category; optionally wired as a CI gate so new PRs cannot introduce CodeFactor findings. Adding the config must not regress existing gates (typecheck, 100% coverage, quality:static, contracts:check)."
